OL,3,CFriend remembers Amy Doherty as
OL,4,C'laughter in the daylight'
OL,6,FMourners at the funeral of Amy Doherty
OL,7,Fhave been told she had a "magnetic
OL,8,Fpersonality" and "would draw people to
OL,9,Fher by her joyful smile".
OL,11,FThe 28-year-old mother was found badly
OL,12,Finjured by police on Saturday and died
OL,13,Flater in hospital.
OL,15,FA 30-year-old man has been arrested on
OL,16,Fsuspicion of murder.
OL,18,FThe funeral mass for Ms Doherty took
OL,19,Fplace on Thursday at Holy Family
OL,20,FChurch in Ballymagroarty, Londonderry.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUpD@LO]pD@ROUqD@XO]
