OL,3,CFriend remembers Amy Doherty as
OL,4,C'laughter in the daylight'
OL,6,FParish priest Fr Joe Gormley told the
OL,7,Fcongregation it was "a very sad day
OL,8,Ffor the family of Amy Doherty, a very
OL,9,Fsad day for our parish and city".
OL,11,FHe said mourners would be thinking of
OL,12,FRhea and Ronan, Ms Doherty's two
OL,13,Fchildren, and would be trying to "make
OL,14,Fsense of the events of last Saturday".
OL,26,@oD@UOUqD@`O]uD@bOUvD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
