PN,44303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1774552271
OL,3,CFriend remembers Amy Doherty as
OL,4,C'laughter in the daylight'
OL,6,FHe said March 21 is a day where, for
OL,7,Fthe first time in six months, "the
OL,8,Ftime of light in our days exceeds the
OL,9,Ftime of darkness", but "the death of
OL,10,FAmy brought a darkness, a sadness,
OL,11,Fanguish deeper than any lack of
OL,12,Fdaylight".
OL,14,FHe said: "The darkness is, in a sense,
OL,15,Fdeeply intensified when we hear the
OL,16,Fhuman story of the beauty of who Amy
OL,17,FDoherty is.
OL,19,F"Amy is a person who has a magnetic
OL,20,Fpersonality who would draw people to
OL,21,Fher by her joyful smile."
OL,26,@oD@_OUqD@QO]qD@XOUtD@IO]vD@JOU{D@AOU}D@
OL,26,AYO]
