OL,3,CFriend remembers Amy Doherty as
OL,4,C'laughter in the daylight'
OL,6,FHe described her as a "dedicated care
OL,7,Fworker" who lifted the spirits of
OL,8,Fpatients at Altnagelvin Hospital, in
OL,9,FDerry, during the pandemic.
OL,11,F"She'd always try and find fun, find
OL,12,Fhumour, particularly in those dark
OL,13,Fdays when people were very afraid," he
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,26,@nD@WOUoD@GO]sD@AOUuD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
