PN,44305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1774552271
OL,3,CFriend remembers Amy Doherty as
OL,4,C'laughter in the daylight'
OL,6,FHe said she helped people set up video
OL,7,Fcalls and encouraged patients to
OL,8,Fconnect with people outside and
OL,9,Fenabled "those who maybe hadn't
OL,10,Fconnected with others for a long time,
OL,11,Fto begin to do so, and to use the
OL,12,Fopportunity of Covid to do that".
OL,14,FHowever, he said, the "heart of her
OL,15,Fcare" was her two children, who "are
OL,16,Fthe centre of our thoughts and prayers
OL,17,Ftoday and beyond".
OL,19,FMs Doherty is survived by her parents,
OL,20,FPatrick and Sharon, and her younger
OL,21,Fbrothers, Shane and Ryan.
OL,26,@qD@IOUtD@`O]vD@WOUwD@EO]wD@aOUyD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
