FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1774552271
OL,3,CFriend remembers Amy Doherty as
OL,4,C'laughter in the daylight'
OL,6,FOn Wednesday the PSNI said the man who
OL,7,Fwas arrested was receiving medical
OL,8,Ftreatment and was not fit for police
OL,9,Finterview.
OL,11,FAccording to Women's Aid, Ms Doherty
OL,12,Fwas the 30th woman in Northern Ireland
OL,13,Fto have been killed since 2020.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
