OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1774552271
OL,3,CFriend remembers Amy Doherty as
OL,4,C'laughter in the daylight'
OL,6,FFr Gormley said "a new culture" needed
OL,7,Fto be built "in the city and society
OL,8,Fand beyond" where "women are honoured,
OL,9,Floved and cherished in the same way as
OL,10,FJesus loved, honoured and cherished
OL,11,Fwomen who knew he could depend on them
OL,12,Fwhen he couldn't depend even on the
OL,13,Fdisciples".
OL,15,FA friend of Ms Doherty, Jasmine, read
OL,16,Fa poem about her which described her
OL,17,Fas "the laughter in the daylight" and
OL,18,F"the warmth of every room".
