OL,3,CFriend remembers Amy Doherty as
OL,4,C'laughter in the daylight'
OL,6,FIt also included the lines "Amy is
OL,7,Fmore than how she left us" and "She's
OL,8,Fnot a shadow, she's not a number, but
OL,9,Fshe's the light she gave so free".
